	<div id="Aboutus" class="main-content about-us section-pad pad-section-new pad-150">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="about-wrapper row">
					<div class="col-md-12">
						<div class="about-text">
							<h2 class="focus-text">About us - Ace Ship Recycling Pte Ltd</h2>
							<p>Ace Ship Recycling Pte Ltd (ASR) was incorporated in January 2014 and is operating out of Singapore. Prior establishing ASR as an individual entity, promoters were 50% stake holders in a JointVenturesince 2008. Majority of our Promoters & Investors are Ship Recyclers from India operating for last 3 decades and have our representatives in London, USA and India.</p>
							<p>We have been at the forefront of Green Recycling, offering end to end solutions of the highest standard. For the same reason, we are associated with JRD Industries which is a ClassNK and Lloyd’s Register (LR) certified HKC Compliant yard in Alang. We have worked with many prestigious ship owners like New Zealand Defence Force, Royal New Zealand Navy, Maersk etc under this association.</p>
							<p>ASR is committed to conducting business according to the highest standards of integrity, in strict compliance with applicable laws and regulations.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
