							<li>Work with trusted, well known brokers in London, Greece, Singapore, Hong Kong, Japan etc.</li>
							<li>Having satisfactorily concluded vessels in volatile markets regularly, ASR is privileged to be considered for repeat business by major ship brokers and owners.</li>
							<li>Buying Delivered & As Is basis.</li>
							<li>Our experienced Technical Managers are able to smoothly handle As Is vessels including reactivation and under tow units</li>
